---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---

<MainLayout title="Membership" description="Join Wessex Whisky Club for exclusive access to premium tastings, member pricing, and early booking privileges">
  
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-r from-amber-50 to-orange-50 py-20">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6">
        Join Wessex Whisky Club
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-slate-700 mb-8">
        Become part of our community and enjoy exclusive access to premium whisky tastings 
        while supporting local charities across the South West.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Membership Benefits -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">Membership Benefits</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Exclusive perks designed for whisky enthusiasts who want to make a difference
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-16">
        <div class="text-center p-6 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-amber-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-amber-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8c-1.657 0-3 .895-3 2s1.343 2 3 2 3 .895 3 2-1.343 2-3 2m0-8c1.11 0 2.08.402 2.599 1M12 8V7m0 1v8m0 0v1m0-1c-1.11 0-2.08-.402-2.599-1"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-3">Member Pricing</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600">
            Enjoy significant discounts on all tasting events compared to guest prices
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="text-center p-6 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-amber-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-amber-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 15v2m-6 4h12a2 2 0 002-2v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2zm10-10V7a4 4 0 00-8 0v4h8z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-3">Early Access</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600">
            Get priority booking for all events and exclusive access to limited tastings
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="text-center p-6 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-amber-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-amber-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-3">Community</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600">
            Connect with fellow whisky enthusiasts and join our member-only events
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="text-center p-6 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-amber-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-amber-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-3">Expert Access</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600">
            Learn from industry experts and distillery representatives at our tastings
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="text-center p-6 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-amber-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-amber-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-3">Charity Impact</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600">
            Regular updates on how your participation supports local charities
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="text-center p-6 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-amber-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-amber-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 6.253v13m0-13C10.832 5.477 9.246 5 7.5 5S4.168 5.477 3 6.253v13C4.168 18.477 5.754 18 7.5 18s3.332.477 4.5 1.253m0-13C13.168 5.477 14.754 5 16.5 5c1.746 0 3.332.477 4.5 1.253v13C19.832 18.477 18.246 18 16.5 18c-1.746 0-3.332.477-4.5 1.253"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-3">Education</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600">
            Access to tasting notes, distillery information, and whisky knowledge resources
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Membership Options -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-slate-50">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">Membership Options</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-slate-600">Choose the membership that works best for you</p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <!-- Annual Membership -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-8 border-2 border-amber-200 relative">
          <div class="absolute -top-4 left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2">
            <span class="bg-amber-600 text-white px-4 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold">Most Popular</span>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">Annual Membership</h3>
            <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-amber-600 mb-1">£25</div>
            <p class="text-slate-600 mb-6">per year</p>
            
            <ul class="text-left space-y-3 mb-8">
              <li class="flex items-center">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-amber-600 mr-3" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                </svg>
                Member pricing on all tastings
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-amber-600 mr-3" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                </svg>
                Priority booking access
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-amber-600 mr-3" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                </svg>
                Member-only events
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-amber-600 mr-3" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                </svg>
                Charity impact reports
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-amber-600 mr-3" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                </svg>
                Significant savings vs guest pricing
              </li>
            </ul>
            
            <button class="w-full bg-amber-600 text-white py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-amber-700 transition-colors font-semibold">
              Join Annual Membership
            </button>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Lifetime Membership -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-8">
          <div class="text-center">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">Lifetime Membership</h3>
            <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-amber-600 mb-1">£150</div>
            <p class="text-slate-600 mb-6">one-time payment</p>
            
            <ul class="text-left space-y-3 mb-8">
              <li class="flex items-center">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-amber-600 mr-3" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                </svg>
                All annual membership benefits
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-amber-600 mr-3" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                </svg>
                Never pay membership fees again
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-amber-600 mr-3" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                </svg>
                VIP treatment at all events
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-amber-600 mr-3" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                </svg>
                Exclusive distillery visits
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-amber-600 mr-3" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                </svg>
                Best value for long-term members
              </li>
            </ul>
            
            <button class="w-full border-2 border-amber-600 text-amber-600 py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-amber-50 transition-colors font-semibold">
              Join Lifetime Membership
            </button>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Additional Info -->
      <div class="mt-12 text-center">
        <p class="text-slate-600 mb-4">
          Have questions about membership? <a href="/contact" class="text-amber-600 hover:text-amber-700 font-semibold">Get in touch</a>
        </p>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-500">
          Membership fees help support our charitable giving and ensure we can continue providing exceptional experiences.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQ Section -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-8">
        <div class="border-b border-slate-200 pb-6">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-2">How much do I save as a member?</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600">Members typically save £10-15 per tasting event compared to guest pricing. With regular attendance, your membership pays for itself quickly.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="border-b border-slate-200 pb-6">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-2">Can I bring guests to events?</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600">Absolutely! Guests are welcome at all our events at the standard guest pricing. It's a great way to introduce friends to our community.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="border-b border-slate-200 pb-6">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-2">What charities do you support?</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600">We select a different local charity each year through member nominations and voting. Past beneficiaries include local hospices, youth centers, and environmental groups.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="border-b border-slate-200 pb-6">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-2">How often are events held?</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600">We typically host 8-12 events per year, ranging from intimate tastings to larger charity events. Members receive advance notice of all events.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-2">Is there a cancellation policy?</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600">We understand plans change. Members can cancel event bookings up to 48 hours before the event for a full refund.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</MainLayout>